<td>The time has come to once again update the "Hot Zones" throughout Norrath. The previous zones have been reverted to their former states and the following zones are now a great place to go for experience and fun: <br />
<br />
* Level 20: Najena <br />
* Level 25: Iceclad Ocean <br />
* Level 30: Rathe Mountains <br />
* Level 35: Frontier Mountains <br />
* Level 40: Gulf of Gunthak <br />
* Level 45: Velketor's Labrynth <br />
* Level 50: Fungus Grove <br />
* Level 55: Old Sebilis <br />
* Level 60: Cazic Thule <br />
<br />
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Effective on February 21, 2006.</td>
